How Taxi Trips Work

  1. GPS track is map-matched to edges
  2. Each edge has fuel consumption (FC)
  3. Trip FC = sum of edge FCs
  4. Edges belong to TAZ zones
  5. Zone-to-zone flows updated

Zone 12 ‚Üí Zone 17: +1 trip
